OL,5, Better mental health support for pupils
OL,6, would be part of Labour's plans to     
OL,7, improve school attendance in England.  
OL,9,FShadow education secretary Bridget     
OL,10,FPhillipson will set out measures later,
OL,11,Fincluding free breakfast clubs for     
OL,12,Fprimary schools.                       
OL,14,FThe plans also include increased       
OL,15,Ffunding for early speech and language  
OL,16,Finterventions.                         
OL,18,FThis week, the government promised to  
OL,19,Fextend the existing attendance-hub     
OL,20,Fscheme to support a thousand more      
OL,21,Fschools in England.                    
